{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Four imps have been <i>imp</i>risoned in one body, and a difficult <i>imp</i>osition has been placed upon them. It seems <i>imp</i>ossible...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227580/extras/Imps.gif?t=1736342012\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Do you remember <i>Fury of the Furries</i>? How about <i>Lost Vikings</i>? <i>Commander Keen</i>? And what about witty adventures like <i>Simon the Sorcerer</i> and <i>Monkey Island</i>? Do you enjoy traumatizing yourself by wallowing in nostalgia for old-school games from the '90s? Well, I sure do! Come, let's have some ale and share memories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227580/extras/The_Rolling_Barrel.gif?t=1736342012\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Implausible Tales</strong> is an adventure puzzle platformer that focuses more on the adventure and puzzle aspects, and less on the platforming. Though, you\u2019ll still need to jump. In each level, you start with one of four imps and must use your wits to find crystals and unlock the others.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Each imp has unique abilities that help you solve puzzles and often deconstruct the level in the process. You\u2019ll frequently need to backtrack and search for previously blocked passages. Each level contains several secrets that aren\u2019t required to complete the game but offer quite a challenge if you want to discover them all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game tries to be funny, but you\u2019ll be the judge of all the puns and fourth-wall breaks...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227580/extras/Cindy_the_Firebird.gif?t=1736342012\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">20+ levels set in various environments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gameplay combining adventure, platforming and puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Charming visual style inspired by classic adventures</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Soundtrack that lingers long after you stop playing</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">That retro game feel, wrapped in a modern engine with full gamepad support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Satire, puns, dad jokes, and other awful things</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Spanish Inquisition</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227580/extras/Skulls.png?t=1736342012\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227580/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736342012","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227580/page.bg.jpg?t=1736342012","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227580/c9cda0b7d145d7fa49678b6849b58894ff9f7aa2/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736342012","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227580/c9cda0b7d145d7fa49678b6849b58894ff9f7aa2/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736342012","categories":[{"descrip